    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can strike two adjacent foes with a single swing.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Str 13, base attack bonus +1.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: As a standard action, you can make a single melee attack against a foe within reach. If you hit, you deal damage normally and can make an additional melee attack (using your full base attack bonus) against a foe that is adjacent to the first and also within reach. You can make only one additional attack per round with this feat. When you use this feat, you take a â€“2 penalty to your Armor Class until your next turn.</span></p>",
